    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80ba-92d0-ed29408cbd4e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The method uses a Depth First Search (DFS) to find sequences that start with a less and assings each learning pathway with the LO it fulfills. REcommendation is a learning path that suggests resources whose LOs will contribute to maximing score (again, constrained by time).  Authors validate their approach first via estimation and secondly in a real setting. In estimation, algorithm outperforms other recommenders. In real setting, it shows that learners advance more in the course than in other e-learning systems.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
